<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Taska - Password Reset</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #dc2626;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            color: #dc2626;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .otp-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fee2e2 0%, #fecaca 100%);
            border: 2px solid #fca5a5;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #991b1b;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .warning-box {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border-left: 4px solid #d97706;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .warning-box ul {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #0284c7;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info-box ol {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #dc2626;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #b91c1c;
        }
        .expiry-notice {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #991b1b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">✓ Taska - Password Reset</div>
        </div>

        <p>Hello <strong>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</strong>,</p>

        <p>We received a request to reset your password for your Taska account. If you didn't make this request, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

        <div class="otp-box">
            <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #991b1b;">Your Password Reset Code</h3>
            <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
            <p class="expiry-notice">⏱️ This code will expire in {{expiryMinutes}} minutes</p>
        </div>

        <div class="warning-box">
            <strong>🔒 Security First:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Never share this code with anyone</li>
                <li>Taska support will never ask for this code</li>
                <li>This code is valid only for password reset</li>
                <li>If you didn't request this, change your password immediately</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #0284c7;">How to Reset Your Password:</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Go to the password reset page on Taska</li>
                <li>Enter your email: <strong>{{email}}</strong></li>
                <li>Enter the code above: <strong>{{otp}}</strong></li>
                <li>Create a new strong password</li>
                <li>Sign in with your new password</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="https://taska-rho.vercel.app/reset-password" class="btn">Reset Password</a>
        </div>

        <div style="background-color: #f3f4f6; border-radius: 5px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <p><strong>💡 Password Tips:</strong></p>
            <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                <li>Use a combination of uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and symbols</li>
                <li>Make it at least 8 characters long</li>
                <li>Avoid using personal information (name, birthdate, etc.)</li>
                <li>Never reuse old passwords</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated password reset request from Taska.</p>
            <p>If you didn't request this reset, your account may be at risk. Please contact our support team immediately.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2026 Taska. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>🚀 Smart Task Management</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 